{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1773352122128,"sessionID":"ses_31bfd06f5ffeleRCi6uuMulALr","part":{"id":"prt_ce405c7ef002uV4tmi3xc6hjWF","sessionID":"ses_31bfd06f5ffeleRCi6uuMulALr","messageID":"msg_ce405bece0011DajpKGm1LGa7m","type":"tool","callID":"toolu_vrtx_011VwGxyVkiygWeYnAfKpdm7","tool":"edit","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-dmux-migration/src/lib/tui.ts","newString":"/**\n * tui.ts — Blessed-based TUI dashboard for Wombo.\n *\n * Layout:\n *   ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n *   │ Header: Wave ID, base branch, mode, model   │\n *   ├──────────────────────────┬──────────────────┤\n *   │ Agent Table              │ Preview Pane     │\n *   │ (selectable rows with    │ (parsed activity │\n *   │  status, activity,       │  stream for the  │\n *   │  progress bars, elapsed) │  selected agent) │\n *   ├──────────────────────────┴──────────────────┤\n *   │ Status bar: keybinds + summary counts       │\n *   └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n *\n * Keybinds:\n *   Up/Down   — navigate agent list\n *   Enter     — attach to selected agent's multiplexer session (interactive mode)\n *   b         — show build log for selected agent\n *   p         — toggle auto-scroll (pause/resume)\n *   q / C-c   — quit\n */","oldString":"/**\n * tui.ts — Blessed-based TUI dashboard for Wombo.\n *\n * Layout:\n *   ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n *   │ Header: Wave ID, base branch, mode, model   │\n *   ├──────────────────────────┬──────────────────┤\n *   │ Agent Table              │ Preview Pane     │\n *   │ (selectable rows with    │ (parsed activity │\n *   │  status, activity,       │  stream for the  │\n *   │  progress bars, elapsed) │  selected agent) │\n *   ├──────────────────────────┴──────────────────┤\n *   │ Status bar: keybinds + summary counts       │\n *   └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n *\n * Keybinds:\n *   Up/Down   — navigate agent list\n *   E